MenuBarTimer v0.2
* GUI change: the main status bar item starts timers. Each timer has its own
status bar item. Pause or stop a timer on its own status bar item.
* A small icon for the main status bar item, instead of the cumbersome text.
* Allow configuring to start MenuBarTimer on login. 

MenuBarTimer v0.1
* A single status bar item to start, pause, stop a single timer (just like
Gnome "Timer-applet").
